   <a class="element-invisible" id="mainContent" tabindex="-1">
    Main Content
   </a>
   <section class="preContent">
    <div class="wrapper">
     <div class="region region-precontent">
      <div class="block block-block" id="block-block-9">
       <div class="content">
        <div class="homebg">
         <p style="text-align:center">
          <img alt="" height="72" src="/files/upload/file_arrowtop.png" width="102"/>
         </p>
        </div>
        <p class="rtecenter">
         Sponsored Programs and Research Compliance (SPaRC) is a comprehensive working group devoted to the management and administration of sponsored programs and open to all who wish to participate. The working group provides central and departmental administrative staff with a platform to exchange and disseminate information related to the support of the sponsored portfolio.
        </p>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
    <!-- end wrapper -->
   </section>
   <!-- end postContent -->
   <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="region region-content">
     <div class="block block-views" id="block-views-upcoming-event-block">
      <h2>
       Upcoming Events
      </h2>
      <div class="content">
       <div class="view view-upcoming-event view-id-upcoming_event view-display-id-block view-dom-id-ff675d4070325eb3249af455df5bad51">
        <div class="view-content">
         <div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first views-row-last">
          <div about="/content/quarterly-meetings" class="ds-1col node node-upcoming-events node-teaser view-mode-teaser clearfix" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document">
           <div class="field field-name-field-event-date field-type-datetime field-label-hidden">
            <div class="field-items">
             <div class="field-item even">
              <span class="date-display-single" content="2019-03-28T00:00:00+00:00" datatype="xsd:dateTime" property="dc:date">
               Thursday, March 28, 2019
              </span>
             </div>
            </div>
           </div>
           <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
            <div class="field-items">
             <div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded">
              <p>
               The
               <strong>
                SPaRC Quarterly Meetings
               </strong>
               aim to provide a platform to exchange and disseminate information related to the support of the sponsored portfolio to central and departmental administrative staff. The meetings include discussions on current research administration topics, updates on policies and procedures, and upcoming events and opportunities.
              </p>
             </div>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="block block-views" id="block-views-announcements-block">
      <h2>
       Announcements
      </h2>
      <div class="content">
       <div class="view view-announcements view-id-announcements view-display-id-block view-dom-id-fb72f0144b903c4865a7e53129520ac6">
        <div class="view-content">
         <div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first views-row-last">
          <div about="/content/new-announcement" class="node node-announcements- node-teaser clearfix" id="node-22" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document">
           <span class="rdf-meta element-hidden" content="New Announcement" property="dc:title">
           </span>
           <span class="rdf-meta element-hidden" content="0" datatype="xsd:integer" property="sioc:num_replies">
           </span>
           <div class="content">
            <div class="field field-name-field-date field-type-datetime field-label-hidden">
             <div class="field-items">
              <div class="field-item even">
               <span class="date-display-single" content="2017-10-02T00:00:00+00:00" datatype="xsd:dateTime" property="dc:date">
                Monday, October 2, 2017
               </span>
              </div>
             </div>
            </div>
            <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
             <div class="field-items">
              <div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded">
               <p>
                Based on NIH's "Interim Guidance on Salary Limitation for Grants and Cooperative Agreements" (not-OD-17-049) and consultations with peer institutions, we would like to advise everyone to increase the NIH salary cap used on proposals from $185,100 to $187,000. This increased amount is consistent within the current Executive Level II of the Federal Executive pay scale, on which NIH's Salary cap is based.
               </p>
              </div>
             </div>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
